969fc15b89f509c65","tid":2492101,"uid":204533,"like":2,"dislike":29,"score":-27,"quote":{"pid":"6a0f731f2b3f2ed74e9a6ed21269bb417ffa6d94","tid":2492101,"uid":50386,"like":42,"dislike":4,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"69e2ba5d66eb988dca8945139246fe789e953588","tid":2492101,"uid":3967,"like":34,"dislike":21,"score":13,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:41:59.000Z","msg":"gym友日日飲"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:59:50.000Z","msg":"做Gym飲蛋白粉<br />\n唔會飲呢啲咖啡因能量飲品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T00:01:52.000Z","msg":"9UP: 其實太多蛋白質對腎都好重負擔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T02:14:57.000Z","msg":"蛋白質一開始會被胃液消化，胃液裡含有酶原的胃蛋白酶原及鹽酸。胃蛋白酶原由胃腺的主細胞分泌，鹽酸是由壁細胞分泌。胃蛋白酶原會在胃裡透過鹽酸活性化，成為胃蛋白酶。從口進入體內的蛋白質，其高級結構被胃液裡的鹽酸破壞，變得容易被蛋白酶分解。一旦蛋白質被胃蛋白酶部分分解後，就會變成多肽（消化蛋白質；peptone）。<br />\n<br />\n蛋白質在十二指腸內的消化胰臟所製造的胰液由十二指腸（小腸的始段）分泌。胰液裡的胰蛋白酶原、胰凝乳蛋白酶原（酶原）分泌至十二指腸，促進腸內的活性化。其中胰蛋白酶原經腸激酶（enterokinase）活化成胰蛋白酶；而胰凝乳蛋白酶原，是經胰蛋白酶活化成胰凝乳蛋白酶。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你一係有慢性腎病<br />\n一係年紀大 功能冇咁勁<br />\n或者你一日食 超過200g 蛋白質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人體蛋白質所需都係每kg x 1.2 <br />\ngym撚x 2<br />\n大前題你唔係百幾kg肥撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8872bd34fe460f625c3df3ff7fef5aad19d1060d","tid":2492101,"uid":30040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"10ac9b7cd41b8414970b2d29d0c18427a6842266","tid":2492101,"uid":289486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T02:10:49.000Z","msg":"一日2L緊係有問題啦<br />\n除左水，乜嘢一日2L都係慢性自殺囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />關red bull咩事"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T02:15:10.000Z","msg":"華Dee每日都飲red bull啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EriH7CXXAAE29LM.jpg:large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEriH7CXXAAE29LM.jpg%3Alarge&h=4be2b701&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f27339aead5ff76a5a05393d80369cd46cf26fc2","tid":2492101,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25434fc96ecce35d65b6edd9b76167c8f3844a04","tid":2492101,"uid":243756,"like":59,"dislike":2,"score":57,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:48:50.000Z","msg":"飲就心悸<br />\n唔飲就嚴重偏頭痛<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係應該一早去醫頭痛咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/door.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/door.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/door.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T02:15:55.000Z","msg":"工作細胞<br />\n咖啡因中毒"},{"pid":"9afb04bd1f5b6246c5b8b0877ab63954234fe0fc","tid":2492101,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb1fd0b36e039906fa897776d8ed93f2325c83cd","tid":2492101,"uid":99930,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:52:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Kq__rOsa1OQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKq__rOsa1OQ&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL2yprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=8899c046\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Kq__rOsa1OQ</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T02:18:31.000Z","msg":"架佬野飲得多都係有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}